This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language understanding tasks such as entity coreference resolution. Additionally, it may also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it discusses neural-based approaches for solving the task. The paper may also be relevant to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it focuses on neural networks, and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as it deals with resolving mentions in a document.
